text: Sunicha is a wonderful person. The massage was amazing. I had really bad shoulder pain and I left feeling so relieved. Hands down best massage ever. They also do couples massages!

Absolutely top tier massage !!! I have had plenty massage before but this is the BEST one yet.  They got every nook and cranny which i needed as someone with WFH back and neck issues.  I love that the hot stones and aromatherapy  are included! I will be a regular here. Very clean. Very friendly. Love it and will definitely be back soon!

As always, excellent experience! I have done the Thai and the Swedish massage multiple times at this location. I was lucky to get a same day appointment today after 24hrs of neck/back spasm and KAI saved the day! Feeling so much better after 90 minutes… I would highly recommend Kai!

So glad I stumbled upon this place, I showed up and asked if they took walk ins- luckily they were able to take me and Hana was amazing. I felt very comfortable with her and after my deep tissue massage there was a noticeable decrease in my pain. Can’t wait to go back! Very reasonable prices too.

This is my 3rd massage here and another amazing experience! The best deep tissue massage around. Frequent check ins for comfort of pressure, stretching that I have not had anywhere else and overall relaxing atmosphere. Ask for Sunicha!
